com.example.a1

Class Task

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.a1.Task
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable

    public class Task
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable
    A representation of a task. A tasks consists of a title, requester's username, description, status, and bid. A tasks can also have photographs and a location added to it.
    See Also:
    User, Status
